fields.name: Liverpool FC Nike Mens 23/24 Home Match Jersey
fields.description:
Liverpool FC are proud to reveal the new LFC Nike Mens 23/24 Home Match Jersey for the 2023/24 season.

Our Match range is an authentic design, the same look worn by the players on the pitch.

White contrast collar & cuffs nod to a jersey worn by the legendary ’74 squad - the re-birth of Shankly’s second team who triumphantly won the FA Cup.

A 97 set between two eternal flames resides on the back of the collar remembers the 97 people who tragically lost their lives at the Hillsborough Disaster.

Our Match collection pairs authentic design details with Nike Dri-FIT technology informed by athlete testing. Moisture-wicking, open-hole fabric in high-heat zones helps Liverpool players and fans alike stay cool and comfortable during intense games or training sessions.
